Open model hub API reference¶

This is the complete API reference of the model hub.

Reference¶

ModelHub([time_aggregation])

The model hub contains collection of data models and convenience functions that you can take, combine and run on Bach data frames to quickly build highly specific model stacks for product analysis and exploration.

SeriesGlobalContexts(engine, base_node, ...)

Objectiv Global Contexts series.

SeriesLocationStack(engine, base_node, ...)

Objectiv Location Stack series.
